      <title>沙特阿美寻求更多中国交易以推动石油化工业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/saudi-aramco-seeks-more-china-deals-in-oil-to-chemicals-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司计划今年和明年在中国投资更多化工厂，以扩大其在中国已达成的交易，从而确保其原油的长期买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/saudi-aramco-seeks-more-china-deals-in-oil-to-chemicals-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
